{"tid":1700162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚去將軍澳追悼會麻煩你入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-08T10:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T11:43:17.000Z","uid":48912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ea16ea2617df7a56c88f6004630ff379d1f8e3","tid":1700162,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"周同學離開左我地，大家會入黎將軍澳追悼<br />\n但唔好忘記將軍澳係好容易有入無出<br />\n所以大家要準備好離開路線<br />\n由其過海巴士廖廖可數<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁講正題</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjhW4G2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjhW4G2.png&h=2742b289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1688939\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1688939</a><br />\n<br />\n上面個POST 出左個陣我半信半疑<br />\n直至下午一堆防暴出現，為左保護狗男女個婚禮<br />\n炸到尚德一堆催淚彈<br />\n最後導致周同學重傷不治<br />\n周同學離開我地，我地當然憤怒<br />\n但憤怒的同時，我地係咪有更多野可以做呢?<br />\n<br />\n上面個post DEL左<br />\n證明左POST 入面的資料係正確<br />\n而老豆搵仔咁辛苦為大家再展示詳細資料<br />\n<br />\n希望周同學你認住呢對狗男女<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699230</a><br />\n<br />\n大家係咪應該為周同學，為老豆搵仔做返DE野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdee51d117218276e8833c7d79189ec0e332854b","tid":1700162,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d990541400050b187694d793a7035fbed366917b","tid":1700162,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f5e07e63d242ffa898ff24c284f7090c057cf0","tid":1700162,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"將軍澳狗屋<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjngkCB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjngkCB.jpg&h=41e6e3f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74c5a0